      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i need to talk to someone about something weird. i think i'm seeing things before they actually happen. like, i saw this specific cracked coffee mug at a cafe this morning and it felt... heavy? like it was vibrating with something. then i turned on the news an hour later and saw a report about a massive collision at a local cafe. i'm starting to think i'm not seeing time the way everyone else does. it's like the future leaves traces on objects. does that make any sense??",
