    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i get the stress part but it doesn't feel like \"intuition\" or some random feeling. it felt physical. like the mug was literally pulling my attention toward what was going to happen. it's not just a hunch, i feel like i'm tuned into a different frequency. like the event already exists and i'm just seeing the shadow of it before the light hits. have you ever heard of people seeing things like this? like actually seeing temporal echoes?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
